name: The Treasure of Tezos - Galactible™ #22
description: Sweet Shiny Gold! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #22, the “Treasure of Tezos!” Deep within the Crypts of Tezos, lies the everlasting spring of gold coins. Hurry! Grab what you can and move quickly, robbers are nearby! Your Mana has been raised by +5,000,000,000 bits! Custom music made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
